      <section eId="sec_CCP-4614">
        <num>CCP 4614</num>
        <heading>4614.  Purchase by co-owner of property or interest sold</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4614__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Any property or interest in the property sold to effect a partition, whether by
licitation or by private sale, may be purchased by a co-owner.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4614__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>If a property or interest in the property is purchased by a co-owner, the co-owner
shall be credited for his share of the property or interest in the property. The co-owner shall
have his share deducted from the purchase price of the property or interest in the property
prior to payment.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112041</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
